high_descs: Turn to the right and move to the table
Pick up the knife from the table
move slightly to the left
Slice the lettuce on the left
Put the knife down between the two heads of lettuce
Pick up a slice of lettuce from the left most lettuce
Turn around and move to the stove to the left
Put the lettuce in a pot
Pick up the left most pot with the lettuce inside
Turn left and move to the sink
Place the pot with the lettuce in the sink
anns.task_desc: Preparing lettuce and putting it in the sink

high_descs: turn to the right go forward go right towards the white table
pick up a knife from the table
turn to the left slice the lettuce that is on the table
put the knife back on the table
pick up a slice of the lettuce that is on the table
turn to the right
go right turn right towards the stove
put the slice of lettuce inside the pot that is on the stove
pick up the stove from the stove
turn to the left across the room
towards the sink put the pot inside the sink
anns.task_desc: slice a lettuce put a slice on a pot put the pot inside the sink

high_descs: Turn right and then back left to get around the refrigerator in front of you then turn right and walk to the table on the opposite side of the room from the refrigerator.
Pick up the knife that is close to the toaster.
Take a step to your left and face the table again.
Use the knife to slice the lettuce closest to the wall.
Place the knife on the table.
Pick up the sliced end of the lettuce.
Travel to the opposite corner of the room and face the stove top.
Place the lettuce slice into the pot on the back left burner.
Pick up the pot with the lettuce in it.
Turn left and walk along the counter until you get to the sink and turn right to face it.
Place the pot with the lettuce slice into the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a pot with lettuce inside it into the sink.
